d%20in%20consulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20decided%20to%20apply%20for%20an%20internship%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20catching%20up%20to%20do.%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20business%20background%2C%20so%20I%20went%20all-in%20on%20prep%20between%20March%20and%20June%20of%20my%20sophomore%20year%20of%20college.%20I%20used%20RocketBlocks%2C%20a%20platform%20for%20consulting%20and%20tech%20interview%20preparation%2C%20attended%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbain-consulting-tips-for-getting-job-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELeland%20bootcamps%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20even%20hired%20a%20coach.%20All%20in%20all%2C%20I%20probably%20spent%20between%20200%20and%20300%20hours%20preparing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20summer%20of%20this%20year%2C%20soon%20after%20I%20turned%2022%2C%20I%20started%20interviewing.%20BCG%20was%20the%20first%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmbb-leaders-consulting-firms-advising-leaders-and-ceos-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsulting%20giants%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20open%20applications.%20I%20sent%20my%20materials%20in%20July%2C%20got%20an%20interview%2C%20and%20had%20an%20offer%20in%20hand%20by%20early%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20thought%20my%20music%20background%20would%20hold%20me%20back.%20I%20even%20tried%20to%20sound%20more%20%26quot%3Bbusinesslike%26quot%3B%20in%20interviews%20%E2%80%94%20using%20buzzwords%20I%20didn't%20fully%20understand%20%E2%80%94%20because%20I%20thought%20that's%20what%20consulting%20firms%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20realized%20that%20wasn't%20the%20best%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20cellist%2C%20I%20spend%20my%20days%20performing%20under%20pressure.%20I%20know%20what%20it%20feels%20like%20to%20make%20mistakes%20in%20front%20of%20an%20audience%20and%20recover%20from%20them.%20I%20also%20know%20how%20to%20collaborate.%20Every%20day%2C%20I%20perform%20in%20small%20ensembles.%20I'm%20constantly%20ada