y%20of%20Emilie%20Karas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f3caf529-7f1e-49a8-962f-140c59c384ec%5C%22%3EAffordable%20'infill'%20housing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EADUs%20and%20mobile%20tiny%20homes%20won't%20solve%20the%20nation's%20housing%20shortage%2C%20particularly%20in%20urban%20areas%20where%20higher-density%20housing%20is%20critical.%20But%20they're%20creating%20much-needed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadu-living-backyard-pros-cons-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaffordable%20housing%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadu-people-share-how-tiny-homes-improved-their-lives-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erenters%20and%20buyers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20in%20neighborhoods%20filled%20with%20single-family%20homes%20on%20large%20lots.%20They%20also%20offer%20homeowners%20a%20way%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-hacking-live-in-adu-rent-out-main-home-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eboost%20their%20property%20values%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20generate%20extra%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaras%2C%20who%20works%20for%20the%20Oregon%20government's%20employment%20department%2C%20charges%20%241%2C500%2C%20including%20utilities%2C%20for%20the%20one-bedroom%20ADU%2C%20%241%2C850%20for%20the%20two-bedroom%20ADU%2C%20and%20%241%2C200%20for%20the%20tiny%20home%20on%20wheels.%20In%20total%2C%20she%20earns%20%244%2C550%20in%20rental%20income%20from%20four%20tenants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaras%20built%20her%20ADUs%20relatively%20cheaply.%20ADU%20construction%20costs%20vary%2C%20typically%20ranging%20between%20%24100%2C000%20and%20%24300%2C000%20per%20unit%2C%20excluding%20permitting%20fees.%20She%20said%20she%20spent%20about%20%24300%2C000%20in%20total%20building%20the%20two%20ADUs%2C%20and%20kept%20costs%20low%20by%20doing%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20interior%20handiwork%20and%20project%20management%20herself.%20She%20estimates%20