y%20guarantees%20that%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Democrats'%20decision%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20government%20over%20free%20health%20care%20for%20illegal%20aliens%20is%20hurting%20all%20Americans%2C%26quot%3B%20Abigail%20Jackson%2C%20a%20White%20House%20spokesperson%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Trump%20Administration%20is%20encouraging%20the%20Democrats%20to%20stop%20the%20pain%20and%20reopen%20the%20government%20with%20the%20bipartisan%20funding%20proposal%20they%20supported%20just%206%20months%20ago%20and%2013%20times%20under%20Biden%20%E2%80%94%20but%20Chuck%20Schumer%20thinks%20every%20day%20of%20the%20shutdown%20'gets%20better.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20workers%20are%20putting%20off%20larger%20expenses%20or%20shaking%20up%20how%20they're%20thinking%20about%20their%20spending.%20One%20Department%20of%20the%20Interior%20worker%20said%20that%20they%20had%20already%20begun%20planning%20for%20a%20potential%20shutdown%20or%20reduction%20in%20force%20in%20February%2C%20pulling%20back%20on%20their%20contributions%20to%20retirement%20accounts%20to%20focus%20instead%20on%20paying%20off%20their%20mortgage.%20Another%20NOAA%20worker%20said%20that%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20secure%20a%20mortgage%20loan%20approval%20to%20potentially%20buy%20a%20new%20house%3B%20that%20fell%20through%20because%20of%20their%20missing%20paycheck.%20And%20a%20NASA%20employee%20in%20a%20dual-federal-worker%20household%20said%20that%20they're%20hitting%20pause%20on%20servicing%20their%20car%20and%20roof%2C%20even%20though%20both%20require%20repairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20scared.%20They%20don't%20know%20how%20they're%20going%20to%20pay%20their%20bills.%20They%20don't%20know%20how%20they're%20going%20to%20put%20food%20on%20the%20table%2C%26quot%3B%20Hornick%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20asking%20about%20unemployment.%20They're%20asking%20about%20whether%20they%20can%20file%20for%20food%20stamps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20are%20also%20turning%20to%20external%20sources%20of%20help%3A%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUSAA%2C%20which%20caters%20to%20military%20households%20and%20offers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usaa.com%2Fsupport%2Fgovernment-shutdown-program%2F%3Fakredirect%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterest-free%20loans%20equivalent%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20paychecks%20for%20impacted%20federal%20workers%2C%20said%20that%20in%20the%2024%20hours%20since%20they%20opened%20the%20program%2C%20they've%20approved%20and%20funded%20nearly%20%2485%20million%20for%20around%2023%2C000%20loans.%20The%20Maryland%20Department%20of%20Labor%20received%20more%20than%20300%20applications%20between%20October%206%20and%20the%20morning%20of%20October%209%20for%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flabor.maryland.gov%2Ffederalworkers%2Fshutdownloan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efederal%20worker%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20the%20Navy%20Federal%20Credit%20Union%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.navyfederal.org%2Fabout%2Fgovernment-shutdown.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoffers%20a%20similar%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20they're%20%26quot%3Bseeing%20a%20significant%20uptick%20in%20participation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20being%20forced%20arbitrarily%20to%20do%20work%20in%20the%20office%20and%20will%20likely%20go%20into%20credit%20card%20or%20loan%20debt%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20NASA%20employee%20who's%20working%20without%20pay%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20miss%20a%20payment%20or%20don't%20pay%20off%20our%20credit%20cards%20because%20we%20don't%20have%20a%20paycheck%2C%20that%20interest%20accrued%20is%20money%20our%20employers%20are%20taking%20away%20from%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgovernment-shutdown-federal-worker-pay-payday-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A