ETech%20leaders%20like%20LinkedIn's%20CEO%20echo%20the%20value%20of%20initiative%20and%20adaptability%20over%20experience.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20AI%20executive's%20interview%20checklist%20has%20three%20simple%20boxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20to%20interview%20across%20all%20kinds%20of%20expertises%2C%26quot%3B%20Scale%20AI's%20interim%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscale-ai-makes-cuts-to-key-team-after-meta-investment-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECEO%20Jason%20Droege%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BLenny's%26quot%3B%20podcast%20released%20on%20Thursday.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20be%20an%20expert%20in%20everything%2C%20and%20so%20I%20reduce%20it%20down%20to%20just%20three%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScale%20helps%20tech%20companies%20like%20Meta%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20xAI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-training-jobs-data-annotators-labelers-outlier-scale-meta-xai-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eimprove%20their%20chatbots%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20doing%20tasks%20like%20rewriting%20bots'%20responses.%20Droege%20took%20on%20the%20role%20of%20Scale's%20interim%20CEO%20in%20June%2C%20after%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Alexandr%20Wang%20left%20the%20startup%20to%20join%20Meta's%20Superintelligence%20Labs.%20Droege%20was%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20Uber%20Eats%20and%20a%20venture%20partner%20at%20Benchmark%20before%20he%20joined%20Scale%20in%202024%20as%20chief%20strategy%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20first%20trait%20he%20looks%20for%20is%20if%20someone%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bcurious%20problem%20solver%26quot%3B%20and%20if%20they%20can%20express%20that%20verbally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDroege%20said%20his%20second%20criterion%20was%20humble%20collaboration.%20He%20gave%20an%20example%20from%20his%20time%20building%20the%20Uber%20Eats%20management%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20I%20would%20hire%20people%2C%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20compose%20almost%20like%20an%20organism%20of%20strengths%20and%20then%20minimize%20the%20conflicts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20he%20said%20he%20looks%20for%20people%20who%20are%20good%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20just%20do%20those%20three%20things%2C%20I%20think%20you%20have%20a%20pretty%20high%20chance%20of%20success%20at%20least%20in%20an%20organization%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20world's%20changing%2C%20right%3F%20So%20you%20do%20need%20people%20that%20are%20adaptable.%20So%20all%20the%20experience%20is%20not%20necessarily%20one-to-one%20relevant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20experience%20is%20important%20for%20some%20expert%20roles%2C%20Droege%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20certain%20roles%2C%20you%20absolutely%20need%20the%20right%20experience%20in%20this%20current%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20see%20this%20with%20researchers%2C%20because%20the%20market's%20moving%20so%20fast%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20time%20to%20train%20up%20some%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDroege%20joins%20several%20tech%20executives%20who%20say%20that%20experience%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20factor%20they%20most%20value%2C%20especially%20with%20AI%20in%20the%20mix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Albert%20Cheng%2C%20the%20former%20head%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fduolingo-former-head-product-top-performers-deep-experience-energy-hiring-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eproduct%20at%20Duolingo%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Grammarly%2C%20said%20that%20top%20performers%20were%20not%20always%20the%20ones%20with%20vast%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20saw%20some%20of%20the%20highest%20performers%20just%20being%20people%20that%20had%20very%20high%20agency%2C%20had%20that%20clock%20speed%2C%20had%20that%20energy%2C