20government%20shutdown.%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Rose%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGreat%20Smoky%20Mountains%20National%20Park%20is%20not%20closed%20during%20the%20government%20shutdown.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELocal%20governments%20in%20North%20Carolina%20and%20Tennessee%20raised%20money%20to%20keep%20it%20staffed%20during%20the%20shutdown.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBefore%20the%20shutdown%2C%20the%20National%20Park%20Service%20said%20two-thirds%20of%20its%20staff%20could%20be%20furloughed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-us-national-parks-for-beginners-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enational%20park%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20staying%20open%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-government-shutdown-impacts-federal-workforce-trump-firings-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egovernment%20shutdown%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Great%20Smoky%20Mountains%20National%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20park%2C%20located%20in%20the%20Appalachian%20Mountains%20between%20North%20Carolina%20and%20Tennessee%2C%20will%20be%20fully%20staffed%20through%20the%20period%2C%20NPR%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outlet%20reported%20that%20seven%20local%20governments%20in%20the%20area%20were%20paying%20the%20park's%20275%20full%20time%20employees%20to%20keep%20the%20park%20operating%20during%20the%20shutdown.%20Local%20governments%20have%20raised%20nearly%20%242%20million%20to%20keep%20the%20park%20running%2C%20per%20NPR.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESevier%20County's%20vice%20mayor%2C%20Bryan%20McCarter%2C%20told%20NPR%20that%20tourism%20from%20the%20park%20boosted%20the%20local%20economy%2C%20so%20the%20park%20must%20be%20kept%20open.%20The%20county%20is%20footing%20much%20of%20the%20bill%20to%20keep%20the%20park%20going%2C%20NPR%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESevier%20County%20is%20located%20in%20the%20foothills%20of%20the%20mountain%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETh