606%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20street%20photo%20of%20Pocaspot%20Myeongdong.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e72bc6cc993f9955cfd891%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222704%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20looked%20up%20guides%20on%20where%20to%20go%20to%20get%20photocards%2C%20and%20Pocaspot%20Myeongdong%20kept%20coming%20up%20on%20TikTok.%20I%20had%20to%20go%20there%20immediately.%3Cp%3ECheryl%20Teh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20first%20reported%20on%20the%20K-pop%20photo%20card%20business%20in%20June.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELast%20month%2C%20I%20took%20a%20trip%20to%20Seoul%2C%20where%20I%20visited%20a%20chain%20of%20stores%20that%20sells%20photocards.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20woman%20beside%20me%20splashed%20out%20%24300%20for%20one%20card.%20I%20spent%20a%20third%20less%20on%20a%20bigger%20haul.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20must%20ask%20you%20not%20to%20judge%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20I%20reported%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bboy%20paper%26quot%3B%20phenomenon%2C%20the%20booming%20business%20of%20K-pop%20photo%20card%20trading.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20a%20casual%20collector%20of%20photo%20cards%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseventeen-joshua-hong-cover-love-is-gone-us-world-tour-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJoshua%20Hong%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20boy%20band%20Seventeen.%20My%20collection%20was%20small%2C%20and%20I%20maintained%20it%20by%20organizing%20swaps%20with%20other%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20said%20at%20the%20time%2C%20with%20great%20gusto%20and%20bravery%2C%20that%20I'd%20never%20become%20a%20person%20who'd%20spend%20more%20than%20%2410%20on%20a%20photocard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20months%20on%2C%20after%20a%20jam-packed%20Seoul%20shopping%20trip%2C%20I%20can't%20say%20that%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20on%20earth%20is%20a%20K-pop%20photocard%3F%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225668%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20Mediheal%20toner%20pads%20on%20the%20shelf%20at%20Olive%20Young.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e72bbe1c1f80efbec53c5c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224251%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMediheal's%20multi-colored%20toner%20pads%20were%20flying%20off%20the%20shelves.%20I%20had%20to%20estimate%20how%20much%20luggage%20space%20I%20had%20left%20before%20loading%20up%20on%20six%20boxes%20of%20the%20stuff.%3Cp%3ECheryl%20Teh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EK-pop%20photocards%20are%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20fan%20merchandise%2C%20and%20a%20boost%20for%20the%20industry's%20bottom%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EK-pop%20fans%20typically%20get%20cards%20free%20with%20the%20purchase%20of%20albums.%20A%20Seventeen%20album%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20can%20come%20with%20two%20to%20four%20random%20photocards%20per%20pack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sprawling%20variety%20aside%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20K-pop%20band%20sometimes%20has%20over%2010%20people%20in%20it%20means%20that%20the%20chances%20of%20pulling%20your%20favorite%20boy%20could%20be%20slim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20randomness%20of%20card%20distribution%20creates%20a%20serious%20business%20for%20collectors%20and%20sellers%20alike.%20Much%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-pokemon-renaissance-dethroned-baseball-cards-trading-psa-grading-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPok%C3%A9mon%20trading%20card%20game%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20limited-edition%20cards%20can%20go%20for%20hundreds%2C%20if%20not%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%2C%20fans%20clamor%20for%20K-pop%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20where%20the%20secondary%20resale%20market%20comes%20in.%20Pocaspot%2C%20a%20TikTok-famous%20business%2C%20is%20a%20chain%20of%20stores%20in%20Seoul%20that%20functions%20like%20a%20seamless%2C%20fangirl-facilitating%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHappy%20scrolling%2C%20fangirl.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225129%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20showing%20a%20buying%20screen%20at%20Pocaspot%20Myeongdong.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e72bc51c1f80efbec53c5e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223847%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20screen%20was%20easy%20to%20navigate%2C%20with%20cards%20sorted%20by%20band%20and%20band%20member.%20You%20could%20also%20filter%20cards%20by%20release%20category.%3Cp%3ECheryl%20Teh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPocaspot%20has%20two%20outlets%20in%20Seoul's%20hottest%20tourist%20districts%2C%20Hongdae%20and%20Myeongdong.%20Each%20outlet%20has%20around%20a%20dozen%20tablets%20through%20which%20orders%20are%20placed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20with%20K-pop%20boyband%20paraphernalia%20hanging%20from%20their%20bags%20gathered%20around%20each%20tablet%20in%20twos%20and%20threes%2C%20shopping%20their%20way%20through%20the%20catalog%20with%20laser%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20joined%20their%20ranks%20and%20scrolled%20through%20a%20seemingly%20endless%20array%20of%20photocards.%20You%20can%20sort%20cards%20by%20band%20and%20band%20member%20for%20easy%20access.%20Customers%20who%20are%20looking%20for%20cards%20from%20lucky%20draws%20and%20limited-release%20runs%20can%20filter%20the%20selection%20via%20a%20dropdown%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20first%20visit%2C%20I%20stood%20there%20for%20over%20an%20hour%20scrolling%20through%20the%20menus%20for%20the%20boy%20bands%20Seventeen%2C%20Stray%20Kids%2C%20and%20BTS%2C%20cross-referencing%20them%20with%20snaps%20of%20my%20personal%20collection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPhotocards%20can%20get%20very%2C%20very%20pricey.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223583%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20shot%20of%20the%20screen%20at%20Pocaspot%20Myeongdong.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e72bc55dbc4fd10daa7fa6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222687%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20of%20these%20photocards%20were%20very%20pricey.%20I%20couldn't%20justify%20shelling%20out%20well%20over%20%24500%20for%20a%20photocard%20of%20Felix%20Lee%2C%20but%20did%20end%20up%20buying%20a%20cheaper%20one.%3Cp%3ECheryl%20Teh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20photocards%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeet-felix-lee-kpop-star-muse-louis-vuitton-artistic-director-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFelix%20Lee%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Stray%20Kids%20member%20and%20LVMH%20muse%2C%20were%20very%20expensive.%20I%20couldn't%20justify%20spending%20over%20500%2C000%20South%20Korean%20won%2C%20or%20%24350%2C%20on%20one%20photocard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeside%20me%2C%20a%20woman%20%E2%80%94%20seemingly%20unfazed%20by%20what%20I%20considered%20an%20eye-watering%20sum%20to%20spend%20on%20a%20piece%20of%20paper%20%E2%80%94%20splashed%20out%20%24300%20for%20a%20photocard%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpop-star-scoups-seventeen-hanbok-met-gala-debut-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESeventeen's%20leader%2C%20S.Coups%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20watched%20in%20awe%20and%20fear%20as%20she%20marched%20up%20to%20the%20cashier%20with%20her%20credit%20card%2C%20and%20resolved%20to%20shop%20within%20my%20income%20bracket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20did%20snap%20up%20a%20selection%20of%20cards%20in%20the%20%245%20to%20%2415%20range.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225317%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20image%20of%20a%20hand%20holding%20a%20box%20of%20products%20from%20Pocaspot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e72bbe1c1f80efbec53c5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223986%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20collected%20my%20loot%20a%20day%20later.%20The%20cards%20had%20been%20placed%20in%20plastic%20protective%20sleeves%2C%20and%20packed%20in%20a%20cute%20box.%3Cp%3ECheryl%20Teh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPocaspot%20says%20on%20its%20website%20that%20it%20has%20over%20a%20million%20K-pop%20photocards%20in%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20it'll%20take%20time%20for%20staff%20to%20locate%20your%20card%20of%20choice.%20I%20was%20shopping%20at%20the%20Myeongdong%20outlet%20after%20the%20day's%20order%20cut-off%20time%20of%204%20p.m.%2C%20so%20I%20picked%20my%20cart%20up%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20opted%20to%20collect%20my%20photocard%20haul%20at%20Pocaspot's%20Hongdae%20branch.%20I%20spent%20just%20over%20%2445%20for%20seven%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frent-samsung-galaxy-phone-fancam-concert-seventeen-korea-kpop-zoom-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ephotocards%20of%20Seventeen's%20Hong%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIf%20you're%20lucky%2C%20you'll%20get%20a%20card%20in%20an%20in-store%20giveaway.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20shot%20of%20a%20randomly%20distributed%20photocard%20of%20Seventeen%20Mingyu%2C%20from%20Pocaspot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e72bc55dbc4fd10daa7fa7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223094%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAs%20a%20reward%20for%20indulging%20in%20Seventeen%20photocards%2C%20I%20was%20also%20gifted%20a%20random%20photocard%20in-store.%3Cp%3ECheryl%20Teh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20traveled%20to%20Seoul%20in%20the%20first%20place%20to%20attend%20the%20opening%20leg%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-seventeen-kpop-boyband-seoul-incheon-concert-merchandise-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESeventeen's%20world%20tour%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20found%20out%20on%20Instagram%20that%20Pocaspot%20had%20organized%20a%20giveaway%20of%20random%20Seventeen%20photocards%2C%20and%20I%20managed%20to%20snag%20one%20at%20the%20Hongdae%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20caved%20to%20temptation%20once%20more%20while%20picking%20up%20my%20first%20order%2C%20buying%20another%20stack%20of%20seven%20photocards%20for%20%2470.%20This%20time%2C%20I%20was%20shopping%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20so%20I%20managed%20to%20pick%20up%20my%20order%20after%207%20p.m.%2C%20the%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPhotocard%20collecting%20is%20not%20for%20the%20faint%20of%20heart.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20shot%20of%20K-pop%20photocards%20fanned%20out%20in%20a%20person's%20hand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e72bc61c1f80efbec53c5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUnboxing%20some%20of%20these%20buys%20was%20a%20true%20joy.%3Cp%3ECheryl%20Teh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECollecting%20cards%20is%20an%20addictive%20and%20costly%20habit%20%E2%80%94%20I%20spent%20over%20%24100%20in%20Seoul.%20The%20desire%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-pokemon-promo-happy-meal-japan-frenzy-pikachu-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecatch%20'em%20all%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20budget-breaking.%20However%2C%20if%20you're%20attempting%20to%20flip%20limited%20edition%20K-pop%20cards%20for%20profit%2C%20you%20can%20get%20them%20graded%20and%20put%20in%20slabs%20for%20maximum%20preservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20I'll%20stick%20to%20my%20cute%20binders%20of%20boy%20paper%20and%20try%20to%20keep%20my%20card%20budget%20as%20low%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheck%20back%20with%20me%20in%20a%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpop-photocard-seventeen-joshua-stray-kids-felix-myeongdong-pocaspot-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760063568000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e72e791c1f80efbec53c91%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpop-photocard-seventeen-joshua-stray-kids-