20BTS.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWork%20trends%20have%20also%20influenced%20how%20people%20consume%20alcohol%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20after-work%20drinks%20on%20Fridays%20were%20a%20big%20cultural%20phenomenon%2C%20and%20older%20people%20were%20more%20used%20to%20consuming%20alcohol%20after%20work%20%26quot%3Bas%20a%20way%20to%20release%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20That's%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsually%20we%20were%20going%20out%20on%20Friday%20nights%2C%20but%20sometimes%20Fridays%20are%20a%20work-from-home%20day%2C%20so%20even%20that%20has%20shifted%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0cf91ba-e26b-4a5c-be2d-3a187a4f7747%5C%22%3EBooze%20businesses%2C%20don't%20despair%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224741%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Various%20cans%20of%20alcoholic%20ready-to-drink%20beverages%20including%20Captain%20Morgan%20Rum%20and%20Coke%2C%20Bacardi%20MoJito%2C%20Archers%20and%20Lemonade%2C%20Malibu%20and%20Pineapple%2C%20Pina%20Colada%20Cocktail%20and%20Gordon's%20Gin%20and%20Tonic%20are%20displayed%20for%20sale%20in%20a%20supermarket.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e4ce775dbc4fd10daa4e9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223556%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20demand%20for%20ready-to-drink%20cocktails%20is%20on%20the%20rise.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Keeble%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20these%20low-energy%20spaces%2C%20like%20picnics%20or%20house%20parties%2C%20people%20continue%20to%20consume%20alcohol%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20we're%20not%20so%20dependent%20on%20the%20high-energy%2C%20high-partying%20moments%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20still%20opportunities%20in%20those%20lower%20energy%20moments%20where%20alcohol%20continues%20to%20play%20a%20role.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%20customer%20trend%2C%20Suntory%20has%20introduced%20more%20%3Ca%20